property.name: text
property.value: The composite actor "Physical" encapsulate the attitude control and dynamics of the quadrotor using a Continuous director. The Sampler and ZeroOrderHold actors allow an interface with a top DE level model. The HlaManager interface and HlaSubscriber & HlaPublisher actors allow to be compliat with HLA standard.
